Wed Jan 13 14:51:04 CET 2021  Flavio Castelli <flavio@castelli.me>

	* Update to release 0.0.2:
		- Add flag to disable automatic registration against the Kubernetes API
		server
		- Add 'insecure' flag: useful to perform benchmarking
		- Better handling of log messages, by default log only Info and Error
		messages. Added a 'debug' flag to be more verbose
